<span id="freeTextContainer17540321378647929546">Wonderfully philosophical. Probing and intelligent, this novel is difficult to be categorised to a specific genre... none seem to be able to adequately contain this novel. We travel from Amsterdam to Cuba, from the 60s to the 90s and from Atheism to Roman Catholicism to Judaism, via Palladio! It&apos;s a massive read and kept me busy for a long time - not helped by the fact that life got in the way... Read this book and prepare to live a little.<br/><br/></span>
