<div id="review_3540467" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3540467" />
    <a title="Jim Coughenour" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/180643-jim-coughenour"><img alt="Jim Coughenour" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1535843128p2/180643.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3540467?book_show_action=true">Jul 25, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jim Coughenour" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jim Coughenour" href="/user/show/180643-jim-coughenour">Jim Coughenour</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/180643-jim-coughenour?shelf=greatfiction">greatfiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3540467" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16910883350155880986">A big fat metaphysical mash-up by the Dutch author of <i>The Assault</i>. Mulisch builds his fantastic tale on the erotic and intellectual entanglements of a <i>menage á trois,</i> enriching the plot of an unabashed thriller with a dazzling array of speculation on everything from mathematics, physics and linguistics to theology and the machinations of the heavenly host.<br/><br/>Next to its spectacular, soaring architecture, <i>The Da Vinci Code</i> is a mouse turd.<br/><br/><br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3540467">
